{"tid":358633,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"跟本而家巴塞最得人驚既係你跟本唔知佢地出左幾多成力","createTime":"2017-08-13T23:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T05:17:12.000Z","uid":38144,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2defe954dae69af45f56e09446f74c916d934c50","tid":358633,"uid":38144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T23:11:16.000Z","msg":"有經常睇疤全場的都知道 <br />\n西甲好多時入夠3-4球就收手 <br />\nMD都散步+眼神防守 <br />\n得S會追下 <br />\n<br />\n今場打比1-3<br />\n其實都係&quot;出奇地&quot;攻足60分鐘 <br />\n剩低30分鐘係到留力 <br />\n費事傷/有牌 <br />\n明眼人都舍其實班友真係hea踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相比鍠狗球玉為左神射手 <br />\n真係90分鐘都出哂奶力勁射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打少一個+入一球真係好威威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5b333befe36e4bc6f5ce46f5388dfdcea7605c","tid":358633,"uid":38144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T23:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/14/071325_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F14%2F071325_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=610c8adc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85745476acadd5985293b26293de0b69081b4fc4","tid":358633,"uid":19556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T23:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a62c728605694b82ecd3be77ce363f54e82937","tid":358633,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T23:40:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aea7ee8284d5c3ab6ec3621d7354b885cc43f591","tid":358633,"uid":4895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T23:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e523fda97253eddcfa20a30a5b01ae5a7c2c2a65","tid":358633,"uid":57291,"like":0,"dislik